{"about_the_game":"<strong>Golel</strong> is a first person dungeon crawler RPG with turn based actions and tile-based movement.<br>Combat is focused on mobility and using the environment to your advantage.<br><strong>Golel</strong> is a disturbing dark fantasy game with horrifying atmosphere.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577730/extras/SkeletonKickGif.gif?t=1737411250\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">STRIDING INTO UNNATURAL REALMS</h2>As a fierce warrior disturbed by your own visions, you willingly chose to venture where no other mortals would dare. <br>You'll encounter many hostile monsters and environments, but also some non-hostile entities that may or may not help you in your quest. <br>Each play-through is unique and set different challenges, obstacles and rewards. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577730/extras/FireBoltGif.gif?t=1737411250\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FAMILIAR YET NEW WAYS TO DO DUNGEON CRAWLING</h2>You will have to use different skills and rely on the environment to gain an advantage. <br>You might drop book shelves on a skeleton, kick a zombie into spikes, or flee through narrow passages in the hopes that the monster hunting you cannot follow. <br>Mobility is important, and you will have to rely on it and tactical use of the environment. Your base stats alone will not save you.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577730/extras/JungleEnvGif.gif?t=1737411250\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DEEP GAMEPLAY</h2>Character development consists of hundreds of different skills, stats and build paths. <br>Different skills and weapons, will unlock different play styles. <br>The world is non linear, and you have some freedom to choose where to travel to.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577730/extras/CaveEnvGif.gif?t=1737411250\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">REPLAYABILITY</h2><strong>Golel</strong> has a 30 hours main campaign.<br>There are many combinations of skills, weapons and attributes, that allow for many different play styles.<br>Every weapon has it's own combat talents and tactics.<br><br>You can be a spell caster, or a mix of both a fighter and a spell caster.<br>This allows to finish the campaign in many different ways.<br><br>Some elements are random generated, while others are hand tailored to provide a unique level design.<br>In addition, a completely procedural generated challenge mode can be played endlessly after finishing the main campaign.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577730/extras/OrcGif.gif?t=1737411250\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577730/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737411250","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577730/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737411250","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577730/d93efad171cd557f5e7e92e5b3a0ab11fe6bab78/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737411250","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2577730/d93efad171cd557f5e7e92e5b3a0ab11fe6bab78/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737411250","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Tracked Controller Support","id":52},{"description":"VR Supported","id":53}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3066000,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<strong>Golel</strong> is a first person dungeon crawler RPG with turn based actions and tile-based movement.<br>Combat is focused on mobility and using the environment to your advantage.<br><strong>Golel</strong> is a disturbing dark fantasy game with horrifying atmosphere.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\